": \"breakers\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3549}, {\"ngram\": \"campus\", \"from\": 3553, \"to\": 3559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They had a club and convinced her to come to a free class a few days later, and she quickly got hooked.\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a club\", \"from\": 3570, \"to\": 3576}, {\"ngram\": \"a free class\", \"from\": 3606, \"to\": 3618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe reason I fell in love with it was because it was so different from gymnastics,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Choi says.\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3755, \"end\": 3759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_Eun-hee\", \"score\": 0.9996609991704456, \"rank\": 0.00033911578969275864, \"text\": \"Choi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_Eun-hee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_Eun-hee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe reason\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3679}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3694}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 3740, \"to\": 3750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy whole life I had been living by this very, very organized list of checked boxes.\", \"from\": 3766, \"to\": 3852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy whole life\", \"from\": 3766, \"to\": 3782}, {\"ngram\": \"this very, very organized list\", \"from\": 3804, \"to\": 3834}, {\"ngram\": \"checked boxes\", \"from\": 3838, \"to\": 3851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What I loved about breaking is that it challenged that.\", \"from\": 3853, \"to\": 3908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It requires you to show up and to figure out who you are and express yourself.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d And no matter how she expressed herself, she was accepted.\", \"from\": 3909, \"to\": 4049, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In that world, she says, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou blend in by not fitting in.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 Choi, 35, graduated from college in 2011.\", \"from\": 4050, \"to\": 4156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4115, \"end\": 4119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_Eun-hee\", \"score\": 0.9996609991704456, \"rank\": 0.00033911578969275864, \"text\": \"Choi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_Eun-hee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_Eun-hee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that world\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4063}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4081}, {\"ngram\": \"college\", \"from\": 4139, \"to\": 4146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She got into marketing, eventually making her way up to global creative operations director for Est\\u00c3\\u00a9e Lauder.\", \"from\": 4157, \"to\": 4267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4260, \"end\": 4266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauder\", \"score\": 0.99996647881904, \"rank\": 3.352230460325233e-05, \"text\": \"Lauder\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauder\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"marketing\", \"from\": 4170, \"to\": 4179}, {\"ngram\": \"her way\", \"from\": 4199, \"to\": 4206}, {\"ngram\": \"global creative operations director\", \"from\": 4213, \"to\": 4248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She kept breaking, working out whenever she could find the time in her busy schedule.\", \"from\": 4268, \"to\": 4353, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 4323, \"to\": 4331}, {\"ngram\": \"her busy schedule\", \"from\": 4335, \"to\": 4352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For 10 years she deftly moved between two worlds, one corporate, one hip-hop.\", \"from\": 4354, \"to\": 4431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"10 years\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4366}, {\"ngram\"