, \"to\": 4652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She clinched her spot in the Olympics when she won gold at the 2023 Pan Am Games.\", \"from\": 4657, \"to\": 4738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her spot\", \"from\": 4670, \"to\": 4678}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4682, \"to\": 4694}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 4708, \"to\": 4712}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 Pan Am Games\", \"from\": 4716, \"to\": 4737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(A country can send up to two B-Girls and two B-Boys; the other U.S. competitor who directly qualified is Victor Montalvo.)\", \"from\": 4739, \"to\": 4862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4845, \"end\": 4851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCA_Records\", \"score\": 0.9999995574217861, \"rank\": 4.425715763630689e-07, \"text\": \"Victor\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCA_Records\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCA_Records\"}, {\"begin\": 4852, \"end\": 4860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Ventura_station\", \"score\": 0.9769238581102762, \"rank\": 0.02362122871543744, \"text\": \"Montalvo\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Ventura_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Ventura_station\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A country\", \"from\": 4740, \"to\": 4749}, {\"ngram\": \"two B-Girls\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4776}, {\"ngram\": \"two B-Boys\", \"from\": 4781, \"to\": 4791}, {\"ngram\": \"the other U.S. competitor\", \"from\": 4793, \"to\": 4818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like Choi, Canada\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s B-Boy Philip Kim, who also earned a \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009923 Pan Am Games gold medal, stumbled into the sport by chancing upon some breakers.\", \"from\": 4864, \"to\": 5008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4869, \"end\": 4873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_Eun-hee\", \"score\": 0.9996609991704456, \"rank\": 0.00033911578969275864, \"text\