"ngram\": \"a bus\", \"from\": 6242, \"to\": 6247}, {\"ngram\": \"the club\", \"from\": 6251, \"to\": 6259}, {\"ngram\": \"the king\", \"from\": 6280, \"to\": 6288}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 6292, \"to\": 6300}, {\"ngram\": \"the right talent\", \"from\": 6312, \"to\": 6328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The battling thing was like,O.K., I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m going to bruise your ego.\", \"from\": 6330, \"to\": 6395, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The battling thing\", \"from\": 6330, \"to\": 6348}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 6364, \"to\": 6369}, {\"ngram\": \"your ego\", \"from\": 6386, \"to\": 6394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I may be broke, but I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m no joke.\", \"from\": 6396, \"to\": 6430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m no joke\", \"from\": 6416, \"to\": 6429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch this.\", \"from\": 6431, \"to\": 6442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Boom!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d (It bears noting that Chambers, who last year put out a kids book calledLil\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 Boogaloo Shrimp and the Clean Sweep,would like to be the Charles Barkley of breaking.)\", \"from\": 6443, \"to\": 6617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6531, \"end\": 6539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boogaloo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.512552468237305e-28, \"text\": \"Boogaloo\", \"types\": [\"Q188451\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boogaloo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boogaloo\"}, {\"begin\": 6540, \"end\": 6546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shrimp\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.986671515728482e-17, \"text\": \"Shrimp\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shrimp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shrimp\"}, {\"begin\": 6588, \"end\": 6603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Barkley\", \"score\": 0.9999999469573609, \"rank\": 5.304280597342251e-08, \"text\": \"Charles Barkley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Barkley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Barkley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chambers\", \"from\": 6474, \"to\": 6482}, {\"ngram\": \"a kids book\", \"from\": 6506, \"to\": 6517}, {\"ngram\": \"the Clean Sweep\", \"from\": 6551, \"to\": 6566}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 6607, \"to\": 6615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Chambers and fellow breaker Adolfo Qui\\u00c3\\u00b1ones threw down against the Electro Rock on film (with a young Ice-T as the DJ), the people in the room decided who won, crowning the winner by acclamation.\", \"from\": 6619, \"to\": 6820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chambers and fellow breaker Adolfo Qui\\u00c3\\u00b1ones\", \"from\": 6624, \"to\": 6668}, {\"ngram\": \"the Electro Rock\", \"from\": 6688, \"to\": 6704}, {\"ngram\": \"film\", \"from\": 6708, \"to\": 6712}, {\"ngram\": \"a young Ice-T\", \"from\": 6719, \"to\": 6732}, {\"ngram\": \"the DJ\", \"from\": 6736, \"to\": 6742}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 6745, \"to\": 6755}, {\"ngram\": \"the room\", \"from\": 6759, \"to\": 6767}, {\"ngram\": \"the winner\", \"from\": 6794, \"to\": 6804}, {\"ngram\": \"acclamation\", \"from\": 6808, \"to\": 6819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sport of Olympic breaking is a wholly different animal.\", \"from\": 6821, \"to\": 6880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sport\", \"from\": 6821, \"to\": 6830}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic breaking\", \"from\": 6834, \"to\": 6850}, {\"ngram\": \"a wholly different animal\", \"from\": 6854, \"to\": 6879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The competitors face off head-to-head, alternating turns in a series of three throw downs, each of which can last up to a minute.\", \"from\": 6882, \"to\": 7011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The competitors\", \"from\": 6882, \"to\": 6897}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 6915, \"to\": 6919}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 6942, \"to\": 6950}, {\"ngram\": \"three throw downs\", \"from\": 6954, \"to\": 6971}, {\"ngram\": \"a minute\", \"from\": 7002, \"to\": 7010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A panel of judges declares the winner.\", \"from\": 7012, \"to\": 7050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A panel\", \"from\": 7012, \"to\": 7019}, {\"ngram\": \"judges\", \"from\": 7023, \"to\": 7029}, {\"ngram\": \"the winner\", \"from\": 7039, \"to\": 7049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are no required moves and while it is literally dancing, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s rarely choreographed.\", \"from\": 7051, \"to\": 7142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no required moves\", \"from\": 7061, \"to\": 7078}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 7114, \"to\": 7120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI only plan about 20 to 30% of a round,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Choi.\", \"from\": 7143, \"to\": 7199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7194, \"end\": 7198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_Eun-hee\", \"score\": 0.9996609991704456, \"rank\": 0.00033911578969275864, \"text\": \"Choi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_Eun-hee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_Eun-hee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about 20 to 30%\", \"from\": 7158, \"to\": 7173}, {\"ngram\": \"a round\", \"from\": 7177, \"to\": 7184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut even then, sometimes that goes out the window and I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll change it right on the spot.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Montalvo, 30, who competes as B-Boy Victor, will plan out three signature moves in each throw down.\", \"from\": 7200, \"to\": 7396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7297, \"end\": 7305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Ventura_station\", \"score\": 0.9769238581102762, \"rank\": 0.02362122871543744, \"text\": \"Montalvo\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Ventura_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Ventura_station\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the window\", \"from\": 7242, \"to\": 7252}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll\", \"from\": 7257, \"to\": 7263}, {\"ngram\": \"B-Boy Victor\", \"from\": 7326, \"to\": 7338}, {\"ngram\": \"three signature moves\", \"from\": 7354, \"to\": 7375}, {\"ngram\": \"each throw\", \"from\": 7379, \"to\": 7389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI try to keep myself 50% structured and then 50% improvised,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he says.\", \"from\": 7397, \"to\": 7472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"50%\", \"from\": 7445, \"to\": 7448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Part of that improvisation is going with the flow, but there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s also a strategic element at play.\", \"from\": 7474, \"to\": 7572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Part\", \"from\": 7474, \"to\": 7478}, {\"ngram\": \"that improvisation\", \"from\": 7482, \"to\": 7500}, {\"ngram\": \"the flow\", \"from\": 7515, \"to\": 7523}, {\"ngram\": \"there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s also a strategic element\", \"from\": 7529, \"to\": 7563}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 7567, \"to\": 7571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOften times I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m responding to the opponent,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Kim.\", \"from\": 7573, \"to\": 7634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7630, \"end\": 7633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.772231935382135e-20, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 7588, \"to\": 7593}, {\"ngram\": \"the opponent\", \"from\": 7608, \"to\": 7620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIn breaking we often talk about having a conversation with movement.\", \"from\": 7635, \"to\": 7706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIn\", \"from\": 7635, \"to\": 7640}, {\"ngram\": \"a conversation\", \"from\": 7677, \"to\": 7691}, {\"ngram\": \"movement\", \"from\": 7697, \"to\": 7705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If someone does a move but I have a better variation of it, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s also showing the judges,Look, he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s adapting in the moment.\", \"from\": 7707, \"to\": 7834, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 7710, \"to\": 7717}, {\"ngram\": \"a move\", \"from\": 7723, \"to\": 7729}, {\"ngram\": \"a better variation\", \"from\": 7741, \"to\": 7759}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 7767, \"to\": 7773}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 7787, \"to\": 7797}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 7823, \"to\": 7833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s also showing that he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s listening to the opponent.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 Kim has an especially deep repertoire of moves\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094avocabulary, in the sport\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s parlance\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094which makes him tough to beat, since judges are on the lookout for a variety of techniques, including: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re using every muscle in your body, basically, in a way that you don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t in your everyday life,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Choi.\", \"from\": 7835, \"to\": 8211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7899, \"end\": 7902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.772231935382135e-20, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 8206, \"end\": 8210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_Eun-hee\", \"score\": 0.9996609991704456, \"rank\": 0.00033911578969275864, \"text\": \"Choi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_Eun-hee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_Eun-hee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 7860, \"to\": 7866}, {\"ngram\": \"an especially deep repertoire\", \"from\": 7906, \"to\": 7935}, {\"ngram\": \"parlance\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094which\", \"from\": 7977, \"to\": 7993}, {\"ngram\": \"judges\", \"from\": 8025, \"to\": 8031}, {\"ngram\": \"the lookout\", \"from\": 8039, \"to\": 8050}, {\"ngram\": \"a variety\", \"from\": 8055, \"to\": 8064}, {\"ngram\": \"techniques\", \"from\": 8068, \"to\": 8078}, {\"ngram\": \"every muscle\", \"from\": 8109, \"to\": 8121}, {\"ngram\": \"your body\", \"from\": 8125, \"to\": 8134}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 8150, \"to\": 8155}, {\"ngram\": \"your everyday life\", \"from\": 8176, \"to\": 8194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re not just walking on your feet.\", \"from\": 8212, \"to\": 8254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your feet\", \"from\": 8244, \"to\": 8253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re upside down, you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re rotating, you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re spinning, you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re sliding.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d That means that in addition to dance work, there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a lot of time spent in the gym.\", \"from\": 8255, \"to\": 8421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 8277, \"to\": 8285}, {\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 8355, \"to\": 8363}, {\"ngram\": \"dance work\", \"from\": 8367, \"to\": 8377}, {\"ngram\": \"there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 8379, \"to\": 8388}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 8398, \"to\": 8402}, {\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 8412, \"to\": 8419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s usually a combination of strength training, explosive work, high intensity interval training\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094things that will help my breaking as well as exercises that will work the antagonist muscles,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Kim.\", \"from\": 8422, \"to\": 8633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8629, \"end\": 8632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.772231935382135e-20, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a combination\", \"from\": 8440, \"to\": 8453}, {\"ngram\": \"strength training\", \"from\": 8457, \"to\": 8474}, {\"ngram\": \"explosive work\", \"from\": 8476, \"to\": 8490}, {\"ngram\": \"high intensity interval training\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094things\", \"from\": 8492, \"to\": 8533}, {\"ngram\": \"my breaking\", \"from\": 8549, \"to\": 8560}, {\"ngram\": \"exercises\", \"from\": 8572, \"to\": 8581}, {\"ngram\": \"the antagonist muscles\", \"from\": 8597, \"to\": 8619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBreaking is a lot of push movements.\", \"from\": 8634, \"to\": 8673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 8649, \"to\": 8654}, {\"ngram\": \"push movements\", \"from\": 8658, \"to\": 8672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I will incorporate a lot of pull movements into my workouts so that I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m not imbalanced with my body.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d While the goal of a breaker is to exert total control over their body, there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s one thing they have zero control of: the music.\", \"from\": 8674, \"to\": 8912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 8696, \"to\": 8701}, {\"ngram\": \"pull movements\", \"from\": 8705, \"to\": 8719}, {\"ngram\": \"my workouts\", \"from\": 8725, \"to\": 8736}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 8745, \"to\": 8750}, {\"ngram\": \"my body.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 8771, \"to\": 8782}, {\"ngram\": \"the goal\", \"from\": 8789, \"to\": 8797}, {\"ngram\": \"a breaker\", \"from\": 8801, \"to\": 8810}, {\"ngram\": \"total control\", \"from\": 8823, \"to\": 8836}, {\"ngram\": \"their body\", \"from\": 8842, \"to\": 8852}, {\"ngram\": \"zero control\", \"from\": 8884, \"to\": 8896}, {\"ngram\": \"the music\", \"from\": 8901, \"to\": 8910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike gymnasts or figure skaters, who arrive with predetermined music, B-Boys and B-Girls are at the mercy of the DJ, who picks the tunes.\", \"from\": 8913, \"to\": 9052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9028, \"end\": 9030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.552224740717365e-14, \"text\": \"DJ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 8920, \"to\": 8928}, {\"ngram\": \"figure skaters\", \"from\": 8932, \"to\": 8946}, {\"ngram\": \"predetermined music\", \"from\": 8964, \"to\": 8983}, {\"ngram\": \"B-Boys\", \"from\": 8985, \"to\": 8991}, {\"ngram\": \"B-Girls\", \"from\": 8996, \"to\": 9003}, {\"ngram\": \"the mercy\", \"from\": 9011, \"to\": 9020}, {\"ngram\": \"the tunes\", \"from\": 9042, \"to\": 9051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only thing competitors know ahead of time is a rough range of beats per minute.\", \"from\": 9053, \"to\": 9136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only thing competitors\", \"from\": 9053, \"to\": 9079}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 9094, \"to\": 9098}, {\"ngram\": \"a rough range\", \"from\": 9102, \"to\": 9115}, {\"ngram\": \"beats\", \"from\": 9119, \"to\": 9124}, {\"ngram\": \"minute\", \"from\": 9129, \"to\": 9135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only does the music selection make preparation tricky, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s also a source of controversy.\", \"from\": 9138, \"to\": 9233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the music selection\", \"from\": 9152, \"to\": 9171}, {\"ngram\": \"preparation\", \"from\": 9177, \"to\": 9188}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 9197, \"to\": 9203}, {\"ngram\": \"controversy\", \"from\": 9221, \"to\": 9232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, because of copyright laws, you won\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t hear any old-school hip-hop, which feeds into the main argument by critics of breaking\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s inclusion in the Olympics: that not enough is done to connect the sport to its roots, especially when it will draw millions of eyeballs.\", \"from\": 9234, \"to\": 9510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9237, \"end\": 9242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2571388585080665e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"copyright laws\", \"from\": 9255, \"to\": 9269}, {\"ngram\": \"any old-school hip-hop\", \"from\": 9288, \"to\": 9310}, {\"ngram\": \"the main argument\", \"from\": 9329, \"to\": 9346}, {\"ngram\": \"critics\", \"from\": 9350, \"to\": 9357}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s inclusion\", \"from\": 9361, \"to\": 9383}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 9387, \"to\": 9399}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 9436, \"to\": 9445}, {\"ngram\": \"its roots\", \"from\": 9449, \"to\": 9458}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 9489, \"to\": 9497}, {\"ngram\": \"eyeballs\", \"from\": 9501, \"to\": 9509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gabriel Dionisio, better known as Kwikstep, grew up breaking in New York City in the 1980s.\", \"from\": 9512, \"to\": 9603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9576, \"end\": 9589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8953911353772197e-34, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": 