": 10132}, {\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 10148, \"to\": 10160}, {\"ngram\": \"the roots\", \"from\": 10167, \"to\": 10176}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 10180, \"to\": 10188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of an event Dionisio will make sure the MC knows the stories of any old school B-Boys who are there, and he sets up a booth where crews can put up old photos.\", \"from\": 10190, \"to\": 10354, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 10199, \"to\": 10207}, {\"ngram\": \"Dionisio\", \"from\": 10208, \"to\": 10216}, {\"ngram\": \"the MC\", \"from\": 10232, \"to\": 10238}, {\"ngram\": \"the stories\", \"from\": 10245, \"to\": 10256}, {\"ngram\": \"any old school B-Boys\", \"from\": 10260, \"to\": 10281}, {\"ngram\": \"a booth\", \"from\": 10312, \"to\": 10319}, {\"ngram\": \"crews\", \"from\": 10326, \"to\": 10331}, {\"ngram\": \"old photos\", \"from\": 10343, \"to\": 10353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cNow it has a social context,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he says.\", \"from\": 10355, \"to\": 10398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a social context\", \"from\": 10369, \"to\": 10385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ken Gabbert is a little more blunt.\", \"from\": 10400, \"to\": 10435, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ken Gabbert\", \"from\": 10400, \"to\": 10411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Ken Swift, he was a pioneering member of the Rock Steady Crew.\", \"from\": 10436, \"to\": 10501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10443, \"end\": 10448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.389421976939505e-19, \"text\": \"Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\"}, {\"begin\": 10484, \"end\": 10500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rock_Steady_Crew\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rock Steady Crew\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rock_Steady_Crew\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rock_Steady_Crew\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pioneering member\", \"from\": 10457, \"to\": 10476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not a sport,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he says.\", \"from\": 10502, \"to\": 10536, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 10516, \"to\": 10523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAn art form that we created with our own terminology and heritage and tradition, all of a sudden for an opportunity, we start calling ourselves athletes and calling this art a sport?\", \"from\": 10537, \"to\": 10722, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our own terminology\", \"from\": 10573, \"to\": 10592}, {\"ngram\": \"heritage\", \"from\": 10597, \"to\": 10605}, {\"ngram\": \"tradition\", \"from\": 10610, \"to\": 10619}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 10641, \"to\": 10655}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 10684, \"to\": 10692}, {\"ngram\": \"this art\", \"from\": 10705, \"to\": 10713}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 10714, \"to\": 10721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s like saying, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Let\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s call basketball a dance now after 75 years.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 As a part of a culture, I look at it from a different perspective.\", \"from\": 10723, \"to\": 10869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Let\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 10745, \"to\": 10755}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 10761, \"to\": 10771}, {\"ngram\": \"a dance\", \"from\": 10772, \"to\": 10779}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 10806, \"to\": 10812}, {\"ngram\": \"a culture\", \"from\": 10816, \"to\": 10825}, {\"ngram\": \"a different perspective\", \"from\": 10845, \"to\": 10868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I look at it artistically, as something that we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve sustained for 50 years to get to this point.\", \"from\": 10870, \"to\": 10967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 10900, \"to\": 10909}, {\"ngram\": \"we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 10915, \"to\": 10922}, {\"ngram\": \"50 years\", \"from\": 10937, \"to\": 10945}, {\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 10956, \"to\": 10966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI love sports.\", \"from\": 10969, \"to\": 10986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI love sports\", \"from\": 10969, \"to\": 10985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I get that.\", \"from\": 10987, \"to\": 10998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But when I was breaking, the whole aspect of doing stuff with my body\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the type of freedom, really connecting to drums and music\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094was different for me.\", \"from\": 10999, \"to\": 11152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 11050, \"to\": 11055}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the type\", \"from\": 11061, \"to\": 11079}, {\"ngram\": \"freedom\", \"from\": 11083, \"to\": 11090}, {\"ngram\": \"drums\", \"from\": 11113, \"to\": 11118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So right now I see what\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s happening.\", \"from\": 11153, \"to\": 11191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 11172, \"to\": 11180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of people act like I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m a hater, but they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re wrong.\", \"from\": 11192, \"to\": 11252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 11192, \"to\": 11197}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 11201, \"to\": 11207}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 11217, \"to\": 11222}, {\"ngram\": \"a hater\", \"from\": 11223, \"to\": 11230}, {\"ngram\": \"they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 11236, \"to\": 11245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s just that I have a culture I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m a part of called hip-hop, and it ain\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t going to change.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Holman\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094who speaks passionately about the community-building and storytelling power of breaking\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094sees both sides of the argument.\", \"from\": 11253, \"to\": 11486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a culture\", \"from\": 11277, \"to\": 11286}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 11287, \"to\": 11292}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 11293, \"to\": 11299}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop\", \"from\": 11310, \"to\": 11317}, {\"ngram\": \"Holman\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094who\", \"from\": 11354, \"to\": 11366}, {\"ngram\": \"the community-building and storytelling power\", \"from\": 11393, \"to\": 11438}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094sees\", \"from\": 11442, \"to\": 11457}, {\"ngram\": \"both sides\", \"from\": 11458, \"to\": 11468}, {\"ngram\": \"the argument\", \"from\": 11472, \"to\": 11484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s in favor of the Olympics (he petitioned to have breaking included in 1984), but he does have concerns about where the sport is headed.\", \"from\": 11487, \"to\": 11639, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"favor\", \"from\": 11508, \"to\": 11513}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 11517, \"to\": 11529}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 11553, \"to\": 11561}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 11598, \"to\": 11606}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 11619, \"to\": 11628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cA lot of these new jack, young breakers, many of them are these incredible gymnasts,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he says.\", \"from\": 11640, \"to\": 11739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these new jack\", \"from\": 11652, \"to\": 11666}, {\"ngram\": \"young breakers\", \"from\": 11668, \"to\": 11682}, {\"ngram\": \"these incredible gymnasts\", \"from\": 11701, \"to\": 11726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not just gymnastics, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s also gyroscopic control over your own body.\", \"from\": 11740, \"to\": 11821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 11759, \"to\": 11769}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 11771, \"to\": 11777}, {\"ngram\": \"also gyroscopic control\", \"from\": 11778, \"to\": 11801}, {\"ngram\": \"your own body\", \"from\": 11807, \"to\": 11820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re doing these moves that are just out of this world.\", \"from\": 11822, \"to\": 11886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these moves\", \"from\": 11842, \"to\": 11853}, {\"ngram\": \"this world\", \"from\": 11875, \"to\": 11885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But are they dancing to the music?\", \"from\": 11887, \"to\": 11921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the music\", \"from\": 11911, \"to\": 11920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou see them going into their routine and they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re on beat, but then they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re going into these moves that are living in their own time and space and have nothing to do with the beats and the rhythm and the melody and the energy and the emotional power of the song and of the music.\", \"from\": 11923, \"to\": 12209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou\", \"from\": 11923, \"to\": 11929}, {\"ngram\": \"their routine\", \"from\": 11950, \"to\": 11963}, {\"ngram\": \"beat\", \"from\": 11981, \"to\": 11985}, {\"ngram\": \"they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 11996, \"to\": 12005}, {\"ngram\": \"these moves\", \"from\": 12017, \"to\": 12028}, {\"ngram\": \"their own time\", \"from\": 12048, \"to\": 12062}, {\"ngram\": \"space\", \"from\": 12067, \"to\": 12072}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 12082, \"to\": 12089}, {\"ngram\": \"the beats\", \"from\": 12101, \"to\": 12110}, {\"ngram\": \"the rhythm\", \"from\": 12115, \"to\": 12125}, {\"ngram\": \"the melody\", \"from\": 12130, \"to\": 12140}, {\"ngram\": \"the energy\", \"from\": 12145, \"to\": 12155}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotional power\", \"from\": 12160, \"to\": 12179}, {\"ngram\": \"the song\", \"from\": 12183, \"to\": 12191}, {\"ngram\": \"the music\", \"from\": 12199, \"to\": 12208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re just doing these moves and challenging someone else to do a move as powerful.\", \"from\": 12210, \"to\": 12297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 12210, \"to\": 12219}, {\"ngram\": \"these moves\", \"from\": 12231, \"to\": 12242}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 12259, \"to\": 12266}, {\"ngram\": \"a move\", \"from\": 12278, \"to\": 12284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t even need music to do it.\", \"from\": 12298, \"to\": 12335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 12320, \"to\": 12325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If your routine can just be done without music, then that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not breaking.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Most young breakers are attuned to the discussion.\", \"from\": 12336, \"to\": 12466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your routine\", \"from\": 12339, \"to\": 12351}, {\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 12377, \"to\": 12382}, {\"ngram\": \"not breaking.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Most young breakers\", \"from\": 12398, \"to\": 12434}, {\"ngram\": \"the discussion\", \"from\": 12450, \"to\": 12464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Montalvo, whose father and uncle were B-Boys in Mexico, says he doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t really like dancing to the music at competitions: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009c\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0089\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Apache\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 [by the Incredible Bongo Band] or James Brown\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Break It Loose\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 remix?\", \"from\": 12467, \"to\